OL,3,CPFAS panel recommends medication for
OL,4,Caffected Jersey residents
OL,6,FJersey's scientific panel on
OL,7,Fperfluoroalkyl and polyfluoroalkyl
OL,8,Fsubstances (PFAS) has recommended
OL,9,Fenhanced testing of islanders who may
OL,10,Fhave been exposed to the chemical.
OL,12,FFirefighters who may have been exposed
OL,13,Fduring the period when it was in use
OL,14,Fin foam in the 90s are the primary
OL,15,Fgroup who should be offered testing,
OL,16,Faccording to the panel.
OL,18,FThey also say wider community testing
OL,19,Fby parish would be beneficial.
