OL,3,CPFAS panel recommends medication for
OL,4,Caffected Jersey residents
OL,6,FDoctor Steve Hajioff, Chair of the
OL,7,FPFAS Scientific Advisory Panel, says:
OL,8,F"We are going to be recommending,
OL,9,Fpotentially, some interventions to
OL,10,Flower PFAS levels in people's bodies.
OL,12,F"Particularly, a sort of tablet that
OL,13,Fis used to lower cholesterol. That's
OL,14,Freally good at taking PFAS down."
OL,16,FStudies have shown that the chemcial
OL,17,Fremains in the body for long periods
OL,18,Fof time and have linked it to certain
OL,19,Ftypes of cancer.
