OL,3,CPFAS panel recommends medication for
OL,4,Caffected Jersey residents
OL,6,FPFAS contaminated several private
OL,7,Fwater supplies in the west of Jersey
OL,8,Fafter leaking from the airport in the
OL,9,F1990s, where it was being used in
OL,10,Ffirefighting foams.
OL,12,FTreatment for PFAS chemicals
OL,14,FThe panel also made several
OL,15,Frecommendations for treating those who
OL,16,Fhad higher levels of PFAS in their
OL,17,Fblood, including cholesterol and bile
OL,18,Fand acid medications to help the body
OL,19,Fget rid of the chemical. Bloodletting
OL,20,Fis suggeested for those who aren't
OL,21,Fsuitable for the medication.
